cs.SI, cs.CY, cs.SD, cs.SOC, cs.CL 

The paper explores the relationship between a community's identity and user engagement in online communities, which involves analyzing language-based typology and mapping almost 300 Reddit communities. This work falls under the scope of social computing (cs.SI), cybernetics (cs.CY), social and information networks (cs.SD), social and behavioral sciences (cs.SOC), and computational linguistics (cs.CL).
